name: Hildbrandt Inkstar Brute and Diablo Complete Tattoo Kit 3
description:
Hildbrandt* The Inkstar' Venture Tattoo Kit 3 is our brand new bare bones package that comes with the basic necessities for learning how to tattoo.  In addition to everything that comes with this package, we include the "Hildbrandt" Tattoo Training DVD, a comprehensive resource on the basics of tattooing. Everything needed to start tattooing. Plenty of supplies as well.


Includes:

razors

pen twin tip

2 transfer carbon sheets

Pack of 50 Hildbrandt Premium Needles:

3RL x 5, 5RL x 5, 7RL x  5, 3RS x 5, 5RS x 5, 7RS x 5, 7M1 x 5, 7M2 x 5, 5RM x 5, 7RM x 5  

2 Aluminum Grip with Tube Stem

12 Disposable Black Tube Tips, matches the needles

5 Pcs Stainless Steel Tube Tips Set 

5 Disposable Black Tube Tips, matches the needles.

Tattoo Machine Adjustment Kit

5 Pairs of Black Latex Gloves

Pack of Rubber Bands

Pack of O Rings

Pack of Grommets

Voltz Power Supply, 110V

1 Clip Cord

1 Sleek Design Foot Pedal.

Medium Size Ink Cups Pack

Small Size Ink Cups Pack

TrueColor* Ink Set, total of 8 colors: Blood Red, Blue Sky, Happy Orange,  Grass Green, Bright Yellow, Very Purple, Crap Brown and Ultra White

Metal Ink Cup Holder

The Brute, a 10 wrap liner/shader

The Diablo 8 wrap liner/shader

Case with lock and key!


USA Quality professional products at a very low price. Do not go spend $150+  (-Do not buy cheap China brands!)

The signature Inkstar short coils allow for lower voltage settings requirements for your power supply, resulting in less chances of the frame heating up.  (There is a 6 month warranty that covers all hardware for these kits, consumables are not covered.)



Fast Shipping!
